Zimaster681, you need to have an account from this site first (it's free, don't worry), then login, lick the download button and you'll get a "(name of this manga).torrent" file.
Next step, google for "utorrent", download it, then start up the "utorrent.exe" that you just got, install the thing.
When you're done, click the "(name of this manga).torrent", 2 displays of utorrent will pop up, click "ok" on the smaller one (you can adjust the download destination folder at "save in", which is on the top left corner of the smaller display).
Now wait until the download finish and go to the destination folder. This may be a little tricky at first, but you'll get used with it in no time. Hope this help.
